    <div class="callout" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <div class="callout-label">What Core Recovery Means</div>
      <p>Each win and loss represents a crossteaming alert response — CT deploying across both Facility and Rebel teams to race against time, reset the core, and hold off both sides simultaneously. A win means the core was saved or the crossteamer was dealt with before the damage became irreversible. A loss means they got there too late. 277 times CT showed up. 224 times it was enough.</p>
    </div>

